{"tid":914164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【英國皇位】皇室受歡迎令英女皇不退位 專家︰佢至少活多10年","createTime":"2018-11-24T04:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T07:52:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bc3182727161274b3c98c6b33c84a19851453547","tid":914164,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:46:10.000Z","msg":"已年屆92歲的英女皇並沒有退位的打算，有研究英國皇室的專家相信，女皇不會在有生之年退位，原因是新一代的皇室成員包括曾孫女夏洛特公主受大眾歡迎，讓女皇不輕言退位，專家又指女皇「至少可活多10年」。<br />\n皇室節目總編輯、皇室得獎紀錄片製作人布倫（Nick Bullen）接受英媒訪問時表示，目前皇室新一代甚受歡迎，令皇室得到人民支持，女皇在這個時刻不會退位。布倫道︰「我認為女皇看得到她孫子和孫媳婦所帶來的(效應)，我甚至想她是否也考慮到曾孫－－夏洛特公主，她已經3歲，已懂得如何應對群眾。」<br />\n早前有報道指，英女皇將會在95歲後將權力下放予皇儲查理斯，讓他出任攝政王。布倫則估計，雖然皇儲查理斯已準備好承接皇位，但屆時他可能已經超過80歲。「女皇的媽媽活到101歲&hellip;&hellip;女皇至少可以活多10年」。<br />\n英女皇的伯父、愛德華八世（King Edward VIII）於1936年為了迎娶美國離婚婦人辛普森（Wallis Simpson）而遜位，是英國皇室史上唯一遜位的君主，由其弟登基成為佐治六世（King George VI），事件一度被視為「遜位危機」。佐治六世是英女皇的父親，他在位16年，於1952年逝世。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181124/large/1543025764_3095.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181124%2Flarge%2F1543025764_3095.jpg&h=d253dd5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181124/58951180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181124%2F58951180&d=uJJZkqHGH4AVduFxQmeqIjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=7b3992b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181124%2F58951180&h=8be6a4ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181124/58951180</a>"},{"pid":"02cd664497f9aa850b63f80ee8a60f4aaf164aa8","tid":914164,"uid":182930,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:54:22.000Z","msg":"查理斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83952e04d0c2766904ed624b440ce5afdcdffa15","tid":914164,"uid":35430,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:56:18.000Z","msg":"我想事頭婆永生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5dbb4a3ca0c45ce8ae5b9591d84ab5df337c246","tid":914164,"uid":150347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02cd664497f9aa850b63f80ee8a60f4aaf164aa8","tid":914164,"uid":182930,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:54:22.000Z","msg":"查理斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:57:12.000Z","msg":"到死都上唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23195e91d5490e2cf8634dc1930b31840ccb1245","tid":914164,"uid":89857,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"分分中佢個仔死左<br />\n事頭婆都未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391c29c8262d4e1ea1b839c5cbd06a403966ff4c","tid":914164,"uid":60655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"02cd664497f9aa850b63f80ee8a60f4aaf164aa8","tid":914164,"uid":182930,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:54:22.000Z","msg":"查理斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:59:19.000Z","msg":"俾個孫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a280cb802c322b6e670849a2fe167c22ade78fb","tid":914164,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T04:59:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3f7b6e111861f61dae49d586ad6cca537b0d9ff","tid":914164,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5dbb4a3ca0c45ce8ae5b9591d84